1. Ja često *posetim* svoju baku. (I often visit my grandmother.)
2. Ona će *posetiti* svoju drugaricu danas. (She will visit her friend today.)
3. Da li ćeš *posetiti* rođake ovog vikenda? (Are you going to visit relatives this weekend?)
4. Oni su *posetili* muzej juče. (They visited the museum yesterday.)
5. Kada su ti roditelji *posetili* grad? (When did your parents visit the city?)
6. Moramo *posetiti* muzej pre nego što odemo. (We have to visit the museum before we leave.)
7. Koliko često *posećuješ* svoje prijatelje? (How often do you visit your friends?)
8. *Poseta* rođaka je uvek prijatna. (A visit from relatives is always pleasant.)
9. Nisam bila u mogućnosti da *posetim* tebe prošle nedelje. (I was unable to visit you last week.)
10. *Posetio* sam nekoliko gradova tokom letovanja. (I visited several cities during my vacation.)